window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When the U.S. Department of Justice permanently disbands the Avenging Angel task force, the books on the operation may close, but former Russian assassin Anya Burinkova knows the real assignment is far from over.</p> <p>Although her efforts alongside Special Agent Gwynn Davis and Supervisory Special Agent Ray White left the Russian mafia bleeding out on the very soil they once commanded, the dragon that is the Bratva is far from beaten. To defeat the ultimate head of the Kremlin-backed organized crime syndicate, Anya must face an enemy she knows far too well—an enemy who stripped her of not only her childhood, but also of the humanity she may never reclaim.</p> <p>Step behind the curtain that once veiled the evil of the former Soviet Union inside the United States, and feel the fury and taste the venom America’s Avenging Angel pours out on her former countrymen as she drives her blade deep into the heart of the Eastern Bloc evil in the thrilling conclusion of the Avenging Angel – Seven Deadly Sins Series.</p>"; 
